theLook eCommerce | Business Intelligence & Statistical Analysis
This project presents a specialized data analysis of theLook, a global eCommerce dataset. It integrates cloud data warehousing with Google BigQuery, advanced statistical computing with Python, and interactive visualization via Looker Studio.

